{"tid":830620,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8旬翁發燒尿不出來　膀胱驚見百顆骰子結石","createTime":"2018-09-21T09:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T10:50:49.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d83701b2dbe690b2d8e9857d6598880f1863e6df","tid":830620,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:51:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_79726d1a1fc599f6b87292131f30d184.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_79726d1a1fc599f6b87292131f30d184.jpg&h=d81f6769&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">醫生開刀從老翁膀胱取出近百顆像骰子形狀的結石，令人嘖嘖稱奇。翻攝畫面</span><br />\n<br />\n台中一名80歲老翁原本就有攝護腺問題，一個晚上有時要起床尿4~5次，但遲遲未就醫，上個月因為突然尿不出來加上高燒不退，家人緊急將他送急診，醫師檢查發現老翁除了攝護腺肥大，膀胱內竟有近百顆結石，藉由內視鏡從尿道進入膀胱將膀胱充水後，再將近百顆約0.5公分的結石從尿道沖出，出來的結石整齊如骰子，好像韓國知名骰子巧克力，讓醫護人員嘖嘖稱奇：「這是骰子結石不是骰子巧克力！」<br />\n<br />\n台中醫院泌尿科醫師林明鋒說，一般結石大多是圓型不規則狀的石頭，少數是不規則狀的鹿角石，但像這種磨成方形骰子狀，而且每一顆都差不多大小的，真的是第一次看到！只是為何老翁結石形狀特別，有護理師開玩笑說是不是「賭神級的擲骰子大王？」林明鋒醫師則笑說「這個結石形狀因人而異，在醫學上真的無法解釋。」<br />\n<br />\n林明鋒指出 , 老翁原本就有攝護腺問題，但是因為遲遲未就醫，所以膀胱反覆發炎感染形成結石，可能有一段時間才會形成這麼多結石，「最近半年就有兩例因為攝護腺肥大未就醫，一就醫就發現百顆腎結石的個案！」幸好患者經過緊急導尿、服用抗生素退燒後，藉由內視鏡順利取出膀胱結石，目前也乖乖定期看診，服用藥物治療攝護腺肥大。<br />\n <br />\n林明鋒提醒，攝護腺肥大好發於50歲以上男性，提醒50歲以上男性只要出現頻尿、排尿困難、尿不乾淨等症狀應該就醫接受治療，大多數可以用藥物控制，嚴重者才需要開刀治療，「結石不治療如反覆發炎尿不乾淨不但可能因為發炎感染造成結石，反覆發炎甚至可能病變導致膀胱癌，一定要小心。」<br />\n <br />\n下周就是中秋節，林明鋒也提醒，結石患者應該要多喝水、控制但白質攝取量，建議有結石家族史或病史朋友，每天至少要喝3千cc開水，中秋烤肉要注意烤魚烤肉的蛋白質攝取量，才能避免結石症狀再復發。(曾雪蒨／台中報導)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_485aae707afdfe138de6789da26d4690.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_485aae707afdfe138de6789da26d4690.jpg&h=155e2c07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180921/640_c49796a79632d8ea8ab6a7774eb7420e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180921%2F640_c49796a79632d8ea8ab6a7774eb7420e.jpg&h=dcab0f96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180921/1434030\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434030&d=Py0fND57G09ATuxmrWDadm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=96c9918f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2Frealtime%2F20180921%2F1434030&h=7da409f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/realtime/20180921/1434030</a>"},{"pid":"24864ad62da72a23aae35caccf21b7f379209c4b","tid":830620,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T09:58:44.000Z","msg":"仲要咁完整<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf208b64f590d80d9ac197415336c72f155eb1a","tid":830620,"uid":204429,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:05:08.000Z","msg":"傳說中腎者之石<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50f815e81badb81fc35f771a5975aa7fae3f5dc4","tid":830620,"uid":194894,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:13:11.000Z","msg":"舍利<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8df5c8e7beb3346390328e6d1a2ecf8ee0897c1","tid":830620,"uid":14696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:16:13.000Z","msg":"好工整喎"},{"pid":"a06e5344dd8b268aa857e4b3d87018e24ff492e4","tid":830620,"uid":48531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"676a27e68c4830de271255f990887aec9e647b75","tid":830620,"uid":79351,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"賭場出千被發現<br />\n之後係條J 到塞番上去"},{"pid":"3e13572e357a975a55335b0ab387a11b4c6f8e9c","tid":830620,"uid":42395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"可唔可以比粒我食"},{"pid":"4d607116df31a18ea6011bd2e2b3cfcdd1c4a159","tid":830620,"uid":44454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e13572e357a975a55335b0ab387a11b4c6f8e9c","tid":830620,"uid":42395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:31:58.000Z","msg":"可唔可以比粒我食"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:34:50.000Z","msg":"你去中藥鋪買人中白"},{"pid":"83079460cb2e472348161b2584e02622cef3d364","tid":830620,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:38:14.000Z","msg":"真係可以整做股仔拎去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651e74451f15d92ab47eaa88cef3cca6061e99fd","tid":830620,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:38:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係可以整做<span style=\"color: red;\">骰</span>仔拎去賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"52edf9d74e2ef5a4900a5614084e5172f0dce056","tid":830620,"uid":178800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:50:49.000Z","msg":"好核突，密集恐懼症"}]}